'''椰撻'''是[[香港|香港]]的一種[[餡餅|餡餅]]<ref name="港式懷舊椰撻">{{cite news |title=港式懷舊椰撻　椰香蛋香30分鐘超簡單 |url=https://www.hk01.com/%E6%95%99%E7%85%AE/201577/%E7%94%9C%E5%93%81%E9%A3%9F%E8%AD%9C-%E6%B8%AF%E5%BC%8F%E6%87%B7%E8%88%8A%E6%A4%B0%E6%92%BB-%E6%A4%B0%E9%A6%99%E8%9B%8B%E9%A6%9930%E5%88%86%E9%90%98%E8%B6%85%E7%B0%A1%E5%96%AE |accessdate=2021-02-22 |work=香港01 |date=2018-06-22 |archive-date=2020-12-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201205000840/https://www.hk01.com/%E6%95%99%E7%85%AE/201577/%E7%94%9C%E5%93%81%E9%A3%9F%E8%AD%9C-%E6%B8%AF%E5%BC%8F%E6%87%B7%E8%88%8A%E6%A4%B0%E6%92%BB-%E6%A4%B0%E9%A6%99%E8%9B%8B%E9%A6%9930%E5%88%86%E9%90%98%E8%B6%85%E7%B0%A1%E5%96%AE |dead-url=no }}</ref>，與[[蛋撻|蛋撻]]非常相似<ref name="人紋椰撻">{{cite news |title=人紋椰撻 |url=https://www.mpweekly.com/culture/%e4%ba%8e%e9%80%b8%e5%a0%af-%e5%b0%88%e6%ac%84-87021 |accessdate=2021-02-22 |work=明周文化 |date=2018-11-22 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200815045056/https://www.mpweekly.com/culture/%E4%BA%8E%E9%80%B8%E5%A0%AF-%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-87021 |archivedate=2020-08-15 |deadurl=no }}</ref>，均為小圓盆狀的餅皮，餡料是[[砂糖|砂糖]]、[[麵粉|麵粉]]、[[雞蛋|雞蛋]]和[[椰絲|椰絲]]混合製成，雞蛋的用量比蛋撻少。由於加入了椰絲，椰撻的餡料充滿[[椰子|椰子]]的香味，而撻面往往會有一顆扁了的[[櫻桃|櫻桃]]<ref>{{cite news |url=http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/supplement/food/art/20091109/13398918 |title=3點3包你食飽 |work= 蘋果日報 |date=2009-11-09 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161201212131/http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/supplement/food/art/20091109/13398918 |archivedate=2016-12-01 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。與蛋撻的另一個分別，就是椰撻只會用[[牛油|牛油]]撻皮而不會用酥皮撻皮<ref>[http://lifestyle.etnet.com.hk/column/index.php/life/homecooking/6246 椰撻] {{Wayback|url=http://lifestyle.etnet.com.hk/column/index.php/life/homecooking/6246 |date=20140216224538 }}，經濟通，21-9-2011</ref>。

相比起蛋撻要剛剛出爐才會有最佳口感，椰撻的味道就較不受溫度影響。

椰撻常見於昔日香港的[[餅店|餅店]]。然而，椰撻的流行程度比不上蛋撻。

